title: Christian Anti-Masturbation’s Mascot “Fappy” Arrested for Public Masturbation?
subtitle: Fappy the Anti-Masturbation Dolphin was not arrested for swimming naked at SeaWorld, because such a mascot does not exist.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: An anti-masturbation mascot named Fappy the Dolphin was arrested for swimming naked with dolphins at a SeaWorld park.
